properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Provincetown MA to Chatham MA to Nantucket MA out 20 nm; Coastal waters east of Ipswich Bay and the Stellwagen Bank National Marine Sanctuary; Coastal Waters extending out to 25 nm South of Marthas Vineyard and Nantucket
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 17 at 6:57PM EST until January 18 at 2:00PM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 2 to 4 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal waters east of Ipswich Bay and the Stellwagen
Bank National Marine Sanctuary, Coastal waters from
Provincetown MA to Chatham MA to Nantucket MA out 20 nm and
Coastal Waters extending out to 25 nm South of Marthas
Vineyard and Nantucket.

* WHEN...Until 2 PM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 2 PM EST SATURDAY... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
